4 Bean Salad
 --@muffinlady
 
Dressing:
1/2 c oil
1/2 c apple cider vinegar
3/4 c sugar
1 tsp salt
1/2 tsp pepper

Combine all ingredients in a bowl and mix until fully incorporated.

Salad:
16 oz green beans, drained and rinsed
16 oz wax beans, drained and rinsed
16 oz kidney or red beans, drained and rinsed
16 oz garbanzo beans, drained and rinsed
1 red onion, diced
3/4 c green pepper
3/4 c celery

Combine all ingredients in a bowl and mix. Add dressing and stir to coat. Refrigerate at least overnight, longer is better (3 days). Toss/stir every once in a while.
